1
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:18,480
Liao Fei.

2
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,480
Let my mom go.

3
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:23,039
Liao Fei.

4
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:25,560
What kind of man hurts a cancer patient?

5
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,680
Come at me if you have a problem.

6
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:29,039
It's all because you stole Xiao Tianman's voice recorder.

7
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:30,160
Give me the recorder.

8
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:30,840
Hurry up!

9
00:01:32,039 --> 00:01:34,560
Liao Fei, if you dare touch my mom,

10
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,960
I swear I'll kill you.

11
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:38,320
Yang Gang, I didn't touch your mom.

12
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,640
Give me the recorder.

13
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,680
I promise your mom will get home safe.

14
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,000
There are so many ways to make money.

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,660
Why do you still risk your life for Xiao Tianman?

16
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:48,920
Liao Fei.

17
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:51,160
Have you ever thought about Liao Yuan?

18
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,039
Let my mom go.

19
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,479
Let my mom go.

20
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:09,120
Don't move! Nobody move! Don't move!

21
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:15,200
Do you want to die?

22
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:21,640
Take me hostage! Hurry!

23
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:26,840
Nobody move!

24
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:30,560
Back off!

25
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,800
Everyone, back off.

26
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,720
Back off. Back off.

27
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:36,000
Back off! Back! Back! Back!

28
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,480
Get back!

29
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:40,020
Yong, untie the rope. Take Mom and go.

30
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,440
Qiang.

31
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,720
Further back! Further back!

32
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:45,980
Hurry! Back over there! Back over there!

33
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,290
Move over there!

34
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,079
Qiang.

35
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:54,880
Don't move.

36
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:58,860
Everyone back.

37
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,080
Go back.

38
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:20,160
Mom, wait until you recover a bit more.

39
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,690
Then we'll go to Guangzhou.

40
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:25,120
Gangzi, are you in some kind of trouble?

41
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,160
No. What trouble could I get into?

42
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,640
Are they trying to hurt you?

43
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,840
No, Mom. No.

44
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,560
No. Nothing's going on, okay?

45
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,240
I know I'm a burden to you.

46
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,680
It must be because of me.

47
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,800
No, Mom. It's not.

48
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:36,960
If they know we're together,

49
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:39,079
they'll use me to threaten you.

50
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:39,880
They won't, Mom. They won't.

51
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:40,960
I already have one foot in the grave.

52
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,320
Mom, stop saying things like that.

53
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,040
Please?

54
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,840
Mom, don't talk like that anymore.

55
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,560
Okay?

56
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,210
I've told you so many times.

57
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,040
Do you think I'd abandon you?

58
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,440
Do you think I could?

59
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,320
Trust me this time, okay?

60
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,600
Just trust me this once.

61
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,680
I believe you.

62
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:19,399
Son, remember.

63
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:22,440
You have a long life ahead of you.

64
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:24,880
You must live an honest life.

65
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,480
Promise me.

66
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,240
You must turn over a new leaf.

67
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,720
Mom, I promise.

68
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,360
I promise.

69
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,200
I'm hungry.

70
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,560
Go buy some food.

71
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:47,130
I'll go buy it for you right now.

72
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,010
Mom, I bought it for you.

73
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:21,880
Mom.

74
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,520
Mom.

75
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,160
Mom.

76
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,520
Mom.

77
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:39,240
Officer, did you find my mom?

78
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:42,680
Yang Gang, we found your mother.

79
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,810
But unfortunately,

80
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,920
she committed suicide by jumping into the river.

81
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,280
When we found her,

82
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,760
she had already passed away.

83
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:56,060
Officer, that's impossible.

84
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,010
There must be a mistake.

85
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,680
It's a mistake. Let me see, Brother.

86
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,080
Brother.

87
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:03,920
Impossible. She couldn't have committed suicide.

88
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:06,280
We were about to go to Guangzhou, you know?

89
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:08,400
We were leaving for Guangzhou soon.

90
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,960
Officer.

91
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:11,880
Stay calm.

92
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:15,720
It is a fact. It cannot be changed.

93
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:32,120
Let me up. Let me up, Brother.

94
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,400
I'll go sit down for a bit.

95
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,720
We can't bring the dead back.

96
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:25,680
Brother.

97
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,640
We're out. I'll get more.
